other_tests.findings: Substantial impairments in attention and working memory; full-scale IQ was determined to be 70 (verbal IQ: 68, performance IQ: 72).
Cavum septum pellucidum and enlargement of the third and fourth ventricles.
Dysmorphic facial features including elongated face with low-set ears, elongated fingers and toes, and flat nasal bridge; oral examination revealed a high-arched palate.
Discussion of genetic findings and implications for future offspring.
